Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.78,0:01:53.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,距离上次见到我的夫君大人已经六年了 学士\N{\fs40}It's been near six years since I last saw my lord husband, Maester.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.70,0:01:57.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我必须得知道……他能活下来吗？\N{\fs40}I must know... will he live?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.58,0:02:01.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他带领船员们冲上一艘伪装过的破船\N{\fs40}He led his sailors into an ambush.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.16,0:02:05.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,结果中了埋伏\N{\fs40}A ship made to look as if it were abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.12,0:02:09.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在战斗中 他被海盗用匕首划伤了脖子\N{\fs40}In the fighting, his neck was slashed by a corsair's dagger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.84,0:02:12.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,掉进了海里\N{\fs40}He fell overboard into the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.30,0:02:14.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,伤势很重\N{\fs40}The wound was severe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.34,0:02:15.97,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,流了很多血\N{\fs40}Much blood was lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.05,0:02:19.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但更令人担忧的是随之而来的高烧\N{\fs40}But the greater concern is the fever that followed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.14,0:02:23.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,随船学士说他是从身体内部烧起来的\N{\fs40}The ship's maester said he burns from within.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.41,0:02:37.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,渡鸦是从哪来的？\N{\fs40}The ravens came in from?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.28,0:02:39.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,暮临厅 公主殿下\N{\fs40}Evenfall, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.28,0:02:42.96,Note_top,,0,0,0,,暮临厅地处风暴地的塔斯岛上，位于风息堡以东，在龙石岛和潮头岛的南方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.83,0:02:42.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,看来他们会在三天后抵达\N{\fs40}So they arrive in three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.33,0:02:48.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,做好一切准备等他回来 凯尔温学士\N{\fs40}Let all be made ready to receive him, Maester Kelvyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.47,0:02:56.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,海蛇向来强壮\N{\fs40}The Sea Snake is strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.72,0:02:58.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,毫无疑问\N{\fs40}No doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.43,0:03:02.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但有些死于血热病人 年纪只有他一半 我就见过\N{\fs40}And yet, I have seen blood fever overcome men half his age.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.56,0:03:05.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不要在我们家乌鸦嘴 魏蒙德\N{\fs40}I will not suffer the talk of crows in my house, Vaemond.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.77,0:03:08.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我爱我哥哥……\N{\fs40}I love my brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.44,0:03:11.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但我们必须面对现实\N{\fs40}but we must be honest with ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.19,0:03:13.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,等我们接到船 他可能已经不在了\N{\fs40}We may greet his ship to find him gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.36,0:03:15.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那由谁来坐上浮木王座呢？\N{\fs40}And who will take the Driftwood Throne?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.90,0:03:17.65,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我外婆正坐得很舒服呢\N{\fs40}My grandmother seems quite comfortable here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.74,0:03:21.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,只有她丈夫不在的时候 她才能代行职责\N{\fs40}She presides only in the absence of her husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.04,0:03:24.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果我哥哥死了 这个位置就该传下去\N{\fs40}On his death, the seat passes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.62,0:03:25.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,传给路斯里斯·瓦列利安\N{\fs40}To Lucerys Velaryon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.79,0:03:27.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,正如我夫君大人所愿\N{\fs40}As is my lord husband's desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.50,0:03:30.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我和海蛇血脉同源\N{\fs40}I am the Sea Snake's own blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.04,0:03:33.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我是他在世上最亲的家人\N{\fs40}the closest kin he has left.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.63,0:03:35.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,注意你的发言 小叔\N{\fs40}Be careful, good-brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.92,0:03:37.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,要是被人听到 可是叛国之罪\N{\fs40}One could take your words for treason.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.52,0:03:49.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我只是说句实话 雷妮丝\N{\fs40}I speak the truth, Rhaenys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.69,0:03:52.03,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而且你心里有数\N{\fs40}And you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.27,0:03:54.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,此事已决\N{\fs40}The matter has been decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.07,0:03:56.99,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,可正是做出这个决定的人\N{\fs40}By a man whose ambition
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.07,0:04:00.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他的野心给我们家族带来了一次又一次的灾难\N{\fs40}has brought down on us calamity after calamity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.74,0:04:03.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我哥哥只在意史书怎么记载\N{\fs40}My brother cares only for the history books.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.16,0:04:08.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但瓦列利安家族的血脉呢？\N{\fs40}But what of the Velaryon line?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.41,0:04:10.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就该这样断绝吗\N{\fs40}Is it to be snuffed out,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.04,0:04:14.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就该被斯壮家的狗崽子们取代吗？\N{\fs40}supplanted by the pups of House Strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.25,0:04:17.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,潮头岛于情于理都应归我所有\N{\fs40}Driftmark is mine by all rights.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:19.80,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,有你支持固然很好\N{\fs40}And while I should like your support,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.88,0:04:22.80,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但我其实并不……需要\N{\fs40}I do not... need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.14,0:04:27.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,风向已经变了\N{\fs40}The winds have shifted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.98,0:04:32.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,朝廷有充分的理由支持我\N{\fs40}The crown has good reason to take my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.44,0:04:35.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我的国王堂弟会为这个拔了你的舌头\N{\fs40}My cousin the King would have your tongue for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.27,0:04:40.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但而今坐在铁王座上的已经不是国王了 嫂子\N{\fs40}But it's not a king who sits the Iron Throne these days, good-sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.16,0:04:42.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是王后\N{\fs40}It's a queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.17,0:07:04.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,征服者和他的姐妹率领一支强大的军队航行\N{\fs40}The Conqueror and his sisters sailed with a great army.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.09,0:07:10.30,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,{\fs40}Se Blākuata Rāsho drāñot vilinio viārtis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.01,0:07:14.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,并在黑水河登陆\N{\fs40}And landed at the Blackwater Rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.60,0:07:15.64,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,{\fs40}Drāñot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.94,0:07:19.48,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,{\fs40}Drāñot. Drāñot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:22.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{\c&H27C0E2&}Drāñot{\c} 是“在末端”？\N{\fs40}{\c&H27C0E2&}Drāñot.{\c} At the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.53,0:07:23.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是河口\N{\fs40}The mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.38,0:07:26.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,河口！加油啊 小杰 你明明知道的\N{\fs40}Mouth! Come on, Jace, you knew that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.95,0:07:29.54,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,{\fs40}Drāñot. Drāñot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.62,0:07:31.39,Subtitle_Valyrian_NOen,,0,0,0,,在河口登陆\N{\fs40}Drāñot vilinio viārtis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.39,0:07:32.79,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,{\fs40}Drāñot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:35.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,{\c&H27C0E2&}Drāñot{\c} 加油啊 小杰\N{\fs40}{\c&H27C0E2&}Drāñot.{\c} Come on, Jace.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.83,0:07:37.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我看今天早上就到这吧\N{\fs40}Perhaps that's enough for this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.46,0:07:39.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不 不 我想继续\N{\fs40}No, no. I want to keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.88,0:07:41.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,学士\N{\fs40}Maester.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.90,0:07:44.55,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,{\fs40}Guēsi misenakson Aegon ūndas.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.42,0:07:48.76,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,伊耿……下令将树……\N{\fs40}Aegon... ordered that the trees should be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.84,0:07:50.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,……杀掉\N{\fs40}...killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.88,0:07:51.76,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,砍掉\N{\fs40}Felled.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.85,0:07:53.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这两个词有关联\N{\fs40}It is a related word.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.85,0:07:55.85,Note_top,,0,0,0,,“misēnakson”意为“被砍倒”；“sēnakson”意为“被杀死”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:56.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我没打算让你一天就学会高等瓦雷利亚语 小杰\N{\fs40}I don't expect you to learn High Valyrian in a day, Jace.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.31,0:07:59.65,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,国王应当以祖先的传统为荣\N{\fs40}A king should honor the traditions of his forbears.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.73,0:08:03.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不过……除非你正打算要废黜自己的母亲\N{\fs40}Well... unless you're planning to depose your own mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.93,0:08:05.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,否则你学习的时间还多着呢\N{\fs40}you have plenty of time to study.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.62,0:08:14.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,退下吧\N{\fs40}Leave us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:18.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,乔佛里……来\N{\fs40}Joffrey... come.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.39,0:08:42.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他是在质疑小路的合法身份\N{\fs40}He means to call into question Luke's legitimacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.56,0:08:45.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,进而质疑小杰\N{\fs40}And by extension Jace,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.48,0:08:47.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,最终质疑我对铁王座的继承权\N{\fs40}and by extension my own claim to the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.69,0:08:51.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,魏蒙德只关心潮头岛和瓦列利安的血脉\N{\fs40}Vaemond cares only about Driftmark and the Velaryon line.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.82,0:08:54.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不关心我们的政治\N{\fs40}Not about our politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:56.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他和奥托·海塔尔达成共识了吗？\N{\fs40}Has he made common cause with Otto Hightower yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.49,0:08:58.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我就担心这个\N{\fs40}This is what I fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.37,0:09:00.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮丝已经飞去宫里了\N{\fs40}Rhaenys has flown to court.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.50,0:09:02.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,当然 她不可能支持他\N{\fs40}Surely, she cannot be planning to back him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:04.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不会的 无论我们之间有什么分歧\N{\fs40}No. Whatever disagreements we may have had,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.21,0:09:05.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她不会那么残忍……\N{\fs40}she's not cruel...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.38,0:09:09.09,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 也不会蠢到那么做 - 分歧？\N{\fs40}-or stupid enough to do that. -Disagreements?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.17,0:09:12.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她认定我们为了结婚害死了她的儿子\N{\fs40}She believes we had her son killed so that we might marry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.30,0:09:16.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是的……但她仍然亲手养大了贝妮拉\N{\fs40}Yes... and yet, she's taken Baela to ward.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.18,0:09:18.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,对 但这是为了兰娜尔 她对咱俩没感情\N{\fs40}Yes. It is Laena's memory she honors. She has no love for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.73,0:09:22.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,毒蛇的毒液已经蔓延这么远了吗？\N{\fs40}Has the vipers' venom spread so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:26.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那些毒蛇正以我父亲的名义统治国家\N{\fs40}Those vipers rule in my father's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.27,0:09:27.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而我父亲——\N{\fs40}And my father--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.78,0:09:36.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我还有什么选择的余地？\N{\fs40}What choice do I have?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.92,0:09:44.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那就去君临吧\N{\fs40}To King's Landing, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.54,0:10:28.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,欢迎坦格利安家族的雷妮拉\N{\fs40}All hail Rhaenyra of House Targaryen,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.79,0:10:31.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,龙石岛公主 铁王座继承人\N{\fs40}Princess of Dragonstone and heir to the Iron Throne
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.51,0:10:34.97,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,以及他的王夫 戴蒙·坦格利安王子\N{\fs40}and her royal consort, Prince Daemon Targaryen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.83,0:11:10.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,欢迎回家 公主殿下\N{\fs40}Welcome back, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.92,0:11:13.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,卡斯威大人\N{\fs40}Lord Caswell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.72,0:11:25.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我本想说回家真好 但我几乎认不出这里了\N{\fs40}I would say it's nice to be home, but I scarcely recognize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.52,0:11:36.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,自打石阶列岛的问题解决以来\N{\fs40}We have continued to enjoy improved customs duties
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.86,0:11:39.15,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们从增长的关税中持续获益\N{\fs40}since the settling of the Stepstones.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.24,0:11:42.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,至于我们能加以利用的份额\N{\fs40}And the extent to which we exploit those
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.33,0:11:46.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,取决于港口总管的收入\N{\fs40}is contingent on the harbor master's receipts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.62,0:11:51.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,关于这个事 呃 那个 修士们再度请求\N{\fs40}Of which, um, uh, the, uh, septons have requested
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.88,0:11:54.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,从中拿出一半\N{\fs40}half that again for a bronze bust
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.26,0:11:57.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,为圣母节定……定制一座青铜半身像\N{\fs40}they wish to co--commission for the, the Festival of the Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.01,0:11:59.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那个 我并不建议批准\N{\fs40}which I would not recommend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.51,0:12:02.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,谢谢您的详尽说明 毕斯柏里大人\N{\fs40}Thank you for that exhaustive accounting, Lord Beesbury.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.47,0:12:03.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我提醒您——\N{\fs40}I remind you--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.19,0:12:13.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您的客人到了 陛下\N{\fs40}Your guests have arrived, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.40,0:12:16.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,依照您的指示 我相信他们得到了\N{\fs40}I trust they've been welcomed as befits their station.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.28,0:12:18.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,和身份相称的接待 首相大人\N{\fs40}As you instructed, Lord Hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.74,0:12:23.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,据我所知 科利斯大人希望他的孙子路斯里斯\N{\fs40}It was my understanding Lord Corlys wished for his grandson Lucerys
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.78,0:12:25.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,继承潮汛之主的头衔\N{\fs40}to succeed him as Lord of the Tides.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.62,0:12:29.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那孩子长到现在 一多半时间都离潮头岛很远\N{\fs40}The boy has been raised most of his life away from Driftmark.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.71,0:12:33.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,确实 他能驾驭龙 但他能指挥舰队吗？\N{\fs40}He can fly a dragon, yes, but can he command a fleet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.09,0:12:35.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,能力不影响他的继承权\N{\fs40}Ability does not alter his claim.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.55,0:12:38.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,海蛇从未为了以防万一\N{\fs40}The Sea Snake has never formally named him as heir,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.59,0:12:39.97,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而正式确定继承人\N{\fs40}if it comes to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.05,0:12:42.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,朝廷必须做出对国家最好的选择\N{\fs40}The crown must choose what is best for the realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.60,0:12:45.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他可是兰尼诺的儿子 有什么根据——\N{\fs40}He is Laenor's son. What grounds could there be--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.43,0:12:47.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就是有什么 毕斯柏里大人\N{\fs40}What indeed, Lord Beesbury.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.56,0:12:49.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就是有什么\N{\fs40}What indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.27,0:12:51.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,明日 我们将听取雷妮拉公主\N{\fs40}We shall hear Princess Rhaenyra's petition,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.85,0:12:53.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,以及其他诉求者的陈情\N{\fs40}along with those of the other claimants on the morrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.98,0:12:56.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 但—— - 请见谅 各位大人\N{\fs40}-But-- -I do beg your pardon, my lords.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.03,0:12:58.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我得去和客人们打个招呼\N{\fs40}I must greet our guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.87,0:13:06.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们要对出售新羊毛征税吗？\N{\fs40}Shall we levy a tax on the sale of new wool?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.74,0:13:08.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陛下……\N{\fs40}Your Grace...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.62,0:13:10.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,有件事情劳您分神\N{\fs40}a matter has arisen that requires your attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.75,0:13:12.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,亚历克爵士 无论是什么 都得等等再说\N{\fs40}Whatever it is, Ser Arryk, it'll need to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.96,0:13:16.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 我是伊利克 陛下 - 当然 抱歉 爵士\N{\fs40}-I'm Erryk, Your Grace. -Of course. My apologies, ser.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.75,0:13:18.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是王子的事\N{\fs40}It's about the Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.46,0:13:21.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他房里的突发状况 非常棘手\N{\fs40}There's been a delicate situation in his apartments.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.00,0:13:54.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,父亲？\N{\fs40}Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.65,0:14:22.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 什么人？ - 父亲\N{\fs40}-Who goes there? -Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.74,0:14:26.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是我 国王陛下\N{\fs40}It's me, my King.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.24,0:14:28.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮拉\N{\fs40}Rhaenyra.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.62,0:14:31.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,噢……\N{\fs40}Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.75,0:14:38.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我和戴蒙来了\N{\fs40}I'm here with Daemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.34,0:14:40.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,戴蒙？\N{\fs40}Daemon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.51,0:14:42.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,戴蒙？\N{\fs40}Daemon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.13,0:14:46.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,戴蒙\N{\fs40}Daemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.89,0:14:51.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,扶我起来\N{\fs40}Help me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.61,0:14:58.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,喔……\N{\fs40}Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.53,0:15:10.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,好久不见了\N{\fs40}It has been so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.21,0:15:20.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,海蛇在石阶列岛打仗 受了重伤\N{\fs40}The Sea Snake has taken a grave wound in battle in the Stepstones.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.63,0:15:23.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,什么时候？\N{\fs40}When?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:25.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们好多年前就赢了啊\N{\fs40}We won that war years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.01,0:15:26.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs40}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.30,0:15:30.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,三城同盟会又回来了\N{\fs40}The Triarchy is resurgent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.56,0:15:33.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,又打起来了\N{\fs40}The fighting is anew.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.48,0:15:35.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而且有人——\N{\fs40}And there is a p--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.18,0:15:38.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,有人陈情 要求裁定潮头岛继承权\N{\fs40}There is a petition to decide upon the succession of Driftmark
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.19,0:15:40.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,以及浮木王座的继承人\N{\fs40}and the heir to the Driftwood Throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.07,0:15:45.07,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陈情？\N{\fs40}Petitions?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.86,0:15:51.07,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,阿莉森和奥托……现在是他们说了算\N{\fs40}Alicent and Otto... they see to all that business now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.16,0:15:53.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不 哥哥 听我说\N{\fs40}No, brother, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.08,0:15:57.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你要声明你的立场\N{\fs40}You are to affirm your position for Lucerys
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.50,0:16:00.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,让路斯里斯成为科利斯·瓦列利安的继承人\N{\fs40}to be Corlys Velaryon's successor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.04,0:16:04.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,科利斯伯爵出什么事了吗？\N{\fs40}Has something happened to Lord Corlys?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.80,0:16:07.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,父亲……\N{\fs40}Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.68,0:16:11.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,有两个人 我们想让您见见\N{\fs40}there's someone we wish to introduce you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.41,0:16:30.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,戴蒙\N{\fs40}Daemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.78,0:16:33.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,哥哥\N{\fs40}Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.79,0:16:38.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那是谁？\N{\fs40}Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.04,0:16:41.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,父亲……\N{\fs40}Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.88,0:16:45.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这是伊耿\N{\fs40}this is Aegon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.26,0:16:48.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,伊耿\N{\fs40}Aegon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.51,0:16:51.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这是……韦塞里斯\N{\fs40}And this... is Viserys.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.43,0:16:56.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,啊……韦塞里斯\N{\fs40}Ah... Viserys.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.23,0:17:04.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这个名字很有王者风范\N{\fs40}Now that is a name fit for a king.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.65,0:17:10.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,哦……\N{\fs40}Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.49,0:17:15.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,哦 哦……\N{\fs40}Oh, oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.53,0:17:16.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,哦 抱歉\N{\fs40}Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.54,0:17:20.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,哦 抱歉 抱歉\N{\fs40}Oh, I'm sorry. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.79,0:17:22.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,抱——\N{\fs40}I'm so--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.84,0:17:28.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我——\N{\fs40}I'm sorry. I'm sor--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.71,0:17:29.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,帮我一下\N{\fs40}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.30,0:17:33.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我的茶 茶\N{\fs40}My tea. My tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.80,0:17:34.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,什么茶？这杯吗？\N{\fs40}What tea? This?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.97,0:17:37.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,对 对\N{\fs40}Yes. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.81,0:17:40.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs40}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.71,0:18:11.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我第一时间把她带来了\N{\fs40}I brought her here immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.38,0:18:13.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,没人看见 王后陛下\N{\fs40}She's seen no one else, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.35,0:18:20.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,过来 亲爱的\N{\fs40}Come here, sweetling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.86,0:18:31.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,告诉我你的名字\N{\fs40}Tell me your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.61,0:18:36.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我叫黛安娜 王后陛下\N{\fs40}It's Dyana, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.83,0:18:40.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,希望您喜欢这名字\N{\fs40}If it please you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.91,0:18:45.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,黛安娜 多美的名字\N{\fs40}Dyana. What a pretty name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.00,0:18:50.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我明白你遇到麻烦了\N{\fs40}I understand you've found yourself in some trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.80,0:18:55.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我当时在给王子送酒\N{\fs40}I was fetching the Prince his wine,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.68,0:18:59.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我把酒放在他的桌子上 当我转身时——\N{\fs40}and I put it on his table, and when I turned--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.60,0:19:02.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我没看见他\N{\fs40}I didn't see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.18,0:19:05.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我请求他停下 陛下\N{\fs40}I asked him to stop, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.44,0:19:08.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我真的求了……\N{\fs40}I did, truly...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.27,0:19:10.15,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您一定要相信我\N{\fs40}you must believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.25,0:19:26.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,谢谢你告诉我 黛安娜\N{\fs40}Thank you for telling me, Dyana.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.42,0:19:33.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 我知道这不是你的过错 - 嗯？\N{\fs40}-I know it wasn't your fault. -Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.80,0:19:37.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我相信你\N{\fs40}I believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.72,0:19:39.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,真——真的吗？\N{\fs40}Y-You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.51,0:19:41.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs40}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.81,0:19:46.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但我担心的是……\N{\fs40}But what I worry about...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.98,0:19:49.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,其他人是否会相信\N{\fs40}is what others might believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.98,0:19:54.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你当时和王子独处一室 是吗？\N{\fs40}You were alone with the Prince, were you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.44,0:19:56.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是的 我——\N{\fs40}Yes, I--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.78,0:19:59.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,没人看见你们俩之间发生了什么\N{\fs40}And no one else saw what happened between the two of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.45,0:20:02.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果其他人听说这件事——\N{\fs40}If anyone else were to hear about this--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.70,0:20:06.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 我没有跟任何人说 - 你告诉了伊利克爵士 塔雅还有我\N{\fs40}-I haven't told anyone. -You told Ser Erryk and Talya and now me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.79,0:20:11.09,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,虽然我相信不是你的错 但其他人可能不会那么相信\N{\fs40}And though I believe you are not to blame, others might not be so trusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.67,0:20:15.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们可能认为你是想败坏王子的名声 或者更糟的是……\N{\fs40}They might think you were trying to besmirch the Prince, or worse...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.59,0:20:19.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,从一开始就是你勾引了他\N{\fs40}that you're the sort of girl that might have enticed him in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.30,0:20:23.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你知道这样的女孩会有怎样的下场\N{\fs40}And you know what happens to girls like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.47,0:20:30.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我一定守口如瓶只字不提 陛下\N{\fs40}I wouldn't dream of breathing another word to anyone, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.15,0:20:33.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我以性命发誓\N{\fs40}I swear it on my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.82,0:20:42.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我知道你不会说的\N{\fs40}I know you won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.25,0:20:56.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一点补偿\N{\fs40}For your troubles.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.35,0:21:06.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,茶来了 陛下\N{\fs40}The tea, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.78,0:21:21.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,最好万无一失\N{\fs40}It's best to be certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.81,0:21:51.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,起床\N{\fs40}Get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.39,0:21:52.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,伊耿！\N{\fs40}Aegon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.77,0:21:56.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,起床！\N{\fs40}Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.53,0:22:01.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,母亲？\N{\fs40}Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.16,0:22:04.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,什么事？\N{\fs40}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.28,0:22:06.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,“什么事？什么事？”\N{\fs40}"What is it? What is it?"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.83,0:22:08.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,“什么事？”你就只会说这一句话？\N{\fs40}"What is it?" That's all you can say for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.62,0:22:09.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,发生什么事了吗？\N{\fs40}Has something happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.08,0:22:12.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,黛安娜\N{\fs40}Dyana.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.71,0:22:15.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那个侍女\N{\fs40}The serving girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.13,0:22:19.09,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,哦 看在诸神的份上\N{\fs40}Oh, for the gods' sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.17,0:22:21.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那个女孩 伊耿 从你身边跑掉的\N{\fs40}The girl, Aegon. The one you sent fleeing from your company.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.67,0:22:24.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,哦 就是找个乐子\N{\fs40}Oh, it was just harmless fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.38,0:22:27.80,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,没什么大不了 她犯不着生气\N{\fs40}She didn't need to go and get upset about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.89,0:22:31.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,想想这给你的妻子和我带来的耻辱\N{\fs40}Think of the shame on your wife, on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.27,0:22:34.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你怎么能一直这样\N{\fs40}How can you keep carrying on like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.60,0:22:36.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,尤其是在今天这样的日子？\N{\fs40}especially on a day like today?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.56,0:22:38.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,怎么了？今天是什么日子？\N{\fs40}Why? What is it today?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.04,0:22:54.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我没你这个儿子\N{\fs40}You are no son of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.80,0:23:03.09,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我也没求着当啊\N{\fs40}I did not ask for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.17,0:23:05.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我做了你要求我做的一切\N{\fs40}I've done everything you've asked me to,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.26,0:23:07.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我这样……\N{\fs40}and I try so...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.43,0:23:10.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我这样努力 但是你和父亲从不满意\N{\fs40}I try so hard, but it will never be enough for you or father.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.14,0:23:17.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你看见黛安娜了吗？ 她本该给孩子们穿衣服的\N{\fs40}Have you seen Dyana? She's supposed to dress the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.44,0:23:27.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他看起来像是变了一个人\N{\fs40}He looks like a different person.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.49,0:23:31.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我认为我们应该再咨询一下格拉底斯学士\N{\fs40}I believe we should also consult Maester Gerardys.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.16,0:23:34.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果他能看看国王 也许会给点不同的建议——\N{\fs40}Perhaps if he could see the King, he'd suggest a different--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.08,0:23:36.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮拉公主\N{\fs40}Princess Rhaenyra.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.21,0:23:37.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,戴蒙王子\N{\fs40}And Prince Daemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.25,0:23:43.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,好久不见 大驾光临 我们万分荣幸\N{\fs40}It has been so long since we were granted the joy of your presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.47,0:23:48.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,的确如此 王后陛下\N{\fs40}Indeed, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.14,0:23:51.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但也没久到值得隆重欢迎的程度\N{\fs40}Though not long enough to merit a greeting upon our arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.64,0:23:54.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我敢肯定王后有要务在身 亲爱的\N{\fs40}I'm sure the Queen had pressing business, my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.43,0:23:57.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,治理国家的事 我们俩又懂什么呢？\N{\fs40}What can either of us know of ruling a kingdom?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.89,0:24:00.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你们很清楚 不是我在治理\N{\fs40}I do not rule, as you well know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.69,0:24:03.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我和我父亲只不过是服务于国王的意志和智慧\N{\fs40}My father and I are mere stewards of the King's will and wisdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.40,0:24:05.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那么国王陛下到底是如何表达智慧的？\N{\fs40}And how exactly is that wisdom expressed?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.90,0:24:09.99,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,通过眨眼和喘气吗？\N{\fs40}In blinks and wheezes?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.07,0:24:11.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他要是还能记住自己的名字 我都要大吃一惊\N{\fs40}I'd be surprised if he could remember his own name.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.83,0:24:13.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 要是你能记住也行 - 自从上次会面之后\N{\fs40}-Or if you could. -King Viserys's condition
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.74,0:24:15.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,韦塞里斯陛下的状况日渐恶化\N{\fs40}has worsened since you saw him last.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.21,0:24:19.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这使他遭受巨大痛苦\N{\fs40}It subjects him to considerable pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.08,0:24:21.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 按照学士们的建议—— - 啊 学士们\N{\fs40}-On the advice of the maesters-- -Ah, the maesters.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.67,0:24:24.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,当然 就是他们让他……\N{\fs40}Of course. It is they who keep him...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.26,0:24:28.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,迷上了罂粟花奶 好叫海塔尔们帮他暖王座\N{\fs40}addled on milk of the poppy while the Hightowers warm his throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.01,0:24:32.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮拉 你是没见过他离开罂粟花奶 痛到不省人事的样子\N{\fs40}Rhaenyra, if you would see him without it, almost blind with suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.80,0:24:36.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,阿莉森 我毫不怀疑 你这样做纯粹是出于仁慈\N{\fs40}Alicent, I have no doubt it was an act of the purest mercy,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.73,0:24:39.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不过告诉我 如果是为了减轻国王的痛苦\N{\fs40}but tell me, for the King's suffering,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.27,0:24:42.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,学士们难道也开了方子 要求去掉坦格利安纹章\N{\fs40}did the maesters also prescribe the removal of Targaryen heraldry
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.36,0:24:44.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,换上各种雕像和七芒星图案？\N{\fs40}and the installation in its stead of various statues and stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.19,0:24:49.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,七神徽章只是为了在未知的道路上引领我们\N{\fs40}The emblems of the Seven serve only to guide us on an uncertain path.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.57,0:24:52.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 提醒我们世间还有更高的权威 - 那么明天\N{\fs40}-To remind us of a higher authority. -And on the morrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.45,0:24:56.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,又是哪位权威将会裁断我儿子对自己遗产的所有权？\N{\fs40}which authority will sit in judgment of my son's claim on his own inheritance?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.04,0:24:59.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,会是我……和国王之手\N{\fs40}That would be mine... and the Hand's.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.83,0:25:01.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但请放心 天父是公正的\N{\fs40}But be assured, the Father is just and commands me
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.88,0:25:05.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他命令我忘记你今天在这间屋子里提出的控诉\N{\fs40}to forget the accusations you have hurled in this room today.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.22,0:25:14.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 比我记忆中要小 - 和我记忆中完全一样\N{\fs40}-Smaller than I remember. -It looks exactly the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.89,0:25:16.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,小路 快来\N{\fs40}Luke, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.91,0:25:34.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,看见了吗？我就说肯定还在\N{\fs40}See? I told you this would still be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.53,0:25:37.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那时候你以为能挥动克里斯顿的流星锤\N{\fs40}And you thought you could swing Criston's morningstar.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.87,0:25:39.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,结果差点搞得脑袋搬家\N{\fs40}And you almost took your own head off.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.34,0:25:48.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 你怎么了？- 人人都在盯着我们\N{\fs40}-What's your problem? -Everyone's staring at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.38,0:25:54.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,没有人会质疑我是潮头岛的继承人……\N{\fs40}No one would question me being heir to Driftmark...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.14,0:25:56.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,假如……\N{\fs40}if...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.18,0:26:00.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,假如我看起来更像兰尼诺·瓦列利安爵士 而不是哈尔温·斯壮爵士\N{\fs40}if I looked more like Ser Laenor Velaryon than Ser Harwin Strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.52,0:26:04.86,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们的想法并不重要\N{\fs40}It doesn't matter what they think.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.65,0:26:51.15,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,干得好 王子\N{\fs40}Well done, my Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.23,0:26:52.65,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你很快就会在比武大会上获胜\N{\fs40}You'll be winning tourneys in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.74,0:26:54.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我才不在乎比武大会\N{\fs40}I don't give a shit about tourneys.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.66,0:26:56.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,两位外甥……\N{\fs40}Nephews...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.33,0:26:59.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你们是来训练的吗？\N{\fs40}have you come to train?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.58,0:27:01.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,开门！\N{\fs40}Open the gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.99,0:27:37.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,保持镇定 王后陛下\N{\fs40}Hold your nerve, my Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.86,0:27:40.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们所做的一切都是为了王国的利益\N{\fs40}What we do, we do for the good of the realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.37,0:27:44.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,必须承认 眼下这事让我非常不安\N{\fs40}I must confess a certain uneasiness now this is at hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.21,0:27:49.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 他可能还活着 - 但如果他已经不在了 我们必须有所准备\N{\fs40}-He may yet live. -But we must be prepared if he does not.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.80,0:28:00.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,归功于杰赫里斯和韦塞里斯的治理\N{\fs40}The realm has enjoyed a long peace,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.68,0:28:03.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,王国已经享有很长一段时间的安定和平\N{\fs40}a credit to the work of both Jaehaerys and Viserys,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.72,0:28:07.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但战争的威胁迫在眉睫 随时会抵达我们的海岸\N{\fs40}but the threat of war looms and may arrive on our shores.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.44,0:28:10.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果战争真的来了 你会想要一个孩子来指挥\N{\fs40}When it does, will you want a child at the command
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.61,0:28:12.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,维斯特洛最强大的舰队吗？\N{\fs40}of the greatest fleet in Westeros?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.57,0:28:16.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,当然了 我们的所作所为\N{\fs40}We must, of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.61,0:28:19.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,必须以臣民利益为重\N{\fs40}act in the interest of our subjects.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.78,0:28:25.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,王后陛下 下一任潮汐之主会知恩图报的\N{\fs40}The next Lord of the Tides will be deeply in your debt, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.29,0:28:27.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,潮头岛也一样会……\N{\fs40}As will Driftmark...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.75,0:28:29.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,全力以赴\N{\fs40}in all its strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.18,0:28:48.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,外婆？\N{\fs40}Grandmother?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.48,0:28:53.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮亚\N{\fs40}Rhaena.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.45,0:29:03.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,贝妮拉说你可能在这里\N{\fs40}Baela said you might be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.41,0:29:07.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你把她照顾得很好\N{\fs40}She's done well as your ward.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.20,0:29:08.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你……\N{\fs40}You've...um...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.79,0:29:11.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,把她养育得出类拔萃\N{\fs40}raised her admirably.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.25,0:29:13.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,过奖了 公主\N{\fs40}You honor me, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.79,0:29:17.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我能和公主单独聊几句吗 雷妮亚？\N{\fs40}Might I speak to the Princess alone, Rhaena?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.72,0:29:21.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,先告退了 公主\N{\fs40}Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.69,0:29:37.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我想了很久 你来这儿的目的是什么\N{\fs40}I wondered for many an hour what your purpose was in coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.32,0:29:40.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,关于魏蒙德爵士的控诉 你到底是站在哪边\N{\fs40}Whether you'd speak for or against the suit brought by Ser Vaemond.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.45,0:29:42.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但是后来我意识到\N{\fs40}But then, I realized...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.24,0:29:45.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你是站在自己这边\N{\fs40}you intend to advocate for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.62,0:29:51.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这次议程是不公平的\N{\fs40}This is no fair proceeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.29,0:29:55.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我打赌这是王后和首相设下的圈套\N{\fs40}It is a trap set by the Queen and the Hand, I'd wager,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.34,0:29:57.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们想借此宣告我的儿子是私生子\N{\fs40}to proclaim my son illegitimate.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.25,0:30:00.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但你对兰尼诺的所作所为更加恶劣\N{\fs40}Yet you did worse than that with Laenor.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.34,0:30:03.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不是吗?\N{\fs40}Did you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.89,0:30:11.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我爱你的儿子\N{\fs40}I loved your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.94,0:30:16.86,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你可能不相信 但我真的爱他\N{\fs40}You may not believe it to be true, but I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.65,0:30:23.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我没有派人杀他\N{\fs40}I did not order his death.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.24,0:30:28.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,也没有参与谋划 我可以发誓\N{\fs40}Nor was I complicit in it. I swear this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.63,0:30:37.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我有个提议\N{\fs40}I'll make you an offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.63,0:30:41.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你支持小路的继承权\N{\fs40}Back Luke's claim,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.92,0:30:44.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,同时让兰娜尔的两个女儿和我的两个儿子订婚\N{\fs40}and let us betroth Laena's children to mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.51,0:30:51.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,贝妮拉将会成为七大王国的王后\N{\fs40}Baela will be Queen of the Seven Kingdoms
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.18,0:30:53.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她的子嗣将会成为铁王座的继承人\N{\fs40}and her sons will be heirs to the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.98,0:30:56.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮亚将统治潮头岛\N{\fs40}Rhaena will rule in Driftmark, and
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.02,0:30:59.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,以后再由她和路斯里斯的孩子继承爵位\N{\fs40}the seat will pass to her and Lucerys's children in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.28,0:31:01.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,慷慨的提议\N{\fs40}A generous offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.99,0:31:06.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 或者说是绝望的提议  - 重要吗?\N{\fs40}-Or a desperate one. -What does it matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.49,0:31:13.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,确实不重要\N{\fs40}You are right in this, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.79,0:31:19.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,至少你说对了这点\N{\fs40}It does not matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.64,0:31:31.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,随你怎么讨价还价\N{\fs40}You can bargain with me all you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.89,0:31:35.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,或是把孙女带过来想让我心软\N{\fs40}Bring my granddaughter with you to soften my resolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.15,0:31:40.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但是明天 海塔尔家族会率先出击\N{\fs40}But tomorrow, the Hightowers land their first blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.19,0:31:44.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们会强迫你屈服\N{\fs40}They force you to your knees...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.32,0:31:47.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而我必定会保持中立\N{\fs40}and I must stand alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.70,0:32:32.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,阿莉森?\N{\fs40}Alicent?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.45,0:32:34.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,阿莉森……\N{\fs40}Alicent...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.04,0:32:37.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,父亲 是我 雷妮拉\N{\fs40}No, it's Rhaenyra, father.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.38,0:32:42.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮拉\N{\fs40}Rhaenyra.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.93,0:32:52.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,冰与火之歌 您相信它会成真吗?\N{\fs40}"The Song of Ice and Fire." Do you believe it to be true?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.01,0:32:56.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,伊耿的梦\N{\fs40}Aegon's Dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.85,0:33:02.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是您告诉我\N{\fs40}You told me
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.56,0:33:06.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,团结整个王国 对抗共同的敌人 是我们的职责\N{\fs40}it was our duty to hold the realm united against a common foe.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.61,0:33:13.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您立我为继承人 却导致王国走向分裂\N{\fs40}By naming me heir, you divided the realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.79,0:33:25.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我以为我想要铁王座\N{\fs40}I thought I wanted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.85,0:33:37.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但这负担太重了\N{\fs40}But the burden is a heavy one.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.56,0:33:42.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,真的太重了\N{\fs40}It's too heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.11,0:33:51.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我……\N{\fs40}My...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.86,0:33:54.86,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我唯一的孩子\N{\fs40}My only child.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.29,0:34:02.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果您想要我担起重任 那就支持我\N{\fs40}If you wish me to bear it, then defend me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.75,0:34:05.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,和我的孩子们\N{\fs40}And my children.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.13,0:34:10.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这……\N{\fs40}It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.85,0:35:08.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,给我准备晚餐 奥托\N{\fs40}I want to have supper, Otto.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.65,0:35:15.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 现在是早上了 陛下  - 今晚\N{\fs40}-It is the morning, Your Grace. -Tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.16,0:35:20.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我所有的家人\N{\fs40}The whole of my family
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.95,0:35:22.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,都在红堡团聚\N{\fs40}are gathered at the Red Keep.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.37,0:35:28.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我希望……我们能一起吃顿饭\N{\fs40}I want us... to dine together.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.87,0:36:01.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,把罂粟花奶拿过来\N{\fs40}Bring milk of the poppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.17,0:36:17.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不要\N{\fs40}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.60,0:36:22.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,安排晚餐就好\N{\fs40}Just arrange the supper.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.73,0:36:29.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,朝廷非常希望\N{\fs40}Though it is the great hope of this court
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.69,0:36:34.07,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,科利斯·瓦列利安大人能够平安归来\N{\fs40}that Lord Corlys Velaryon survive his wounds,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.15,0:36:36.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但我们聚集在此 有着更加沉重的任务\N{\fs40}we gather here with the grim task
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.61,0:36:39.15,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那就是解决潮头岛的继承人问题\N{\fs40}of dealing with the succession of Driftmark.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.41,0:36:43.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,作为首相 我代表国王就此事\N{\fs40}As Hand, I speak with the King's voice on this
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.66,0:36:45.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,和其他所有问题发言\N{\fs40}and all other matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.58,0:36:49.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,朝廷现在开始听取陈情\N{\fs40}The crown will now hear the petitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.67,0:36:52.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,瓦列利安家族的魏蒙德爵士\N{\fs40}Ser Vaemond of House Velaryon.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.93,0:37:02.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,王后陛下\N{\fs40}My Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.51,0:37:04.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,首相大人\N{\fs40}My Lord Hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.93,0:37:09.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们家族的历史可以从七大王国\N{\fs40}The history of our noble houses extends beyond the Seven Kingdoms
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.10,0:37:11.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一直追溯到古瓦雷利亚时代\N{\fs40}to the days of Old Valyria.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.40,0:37:14.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,坦格利安家族一直统治着天空\N{\fs40}For as long as House Targaryen has ruled the skies,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.27,0:37:16.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,正如瓦列利安家族统治着海洋\N{\fs40}House Velaryon has ruled the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.98,0:37:21.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,瓦雷利亚末日浩劫之后 我们两个家族成为最后的幸存者\N{\fs40}When the Doom fell on Valyria, our houses became the last of their kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.57,0:37:24.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们的祖先来到这片全新的土地 他们知道如果失败\N{\fs40}Our forebearers came to this new land, knowing that were they to fail,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.99,0:37:28.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,将意味着血脉和姓氏的终结\N{\fs40}it would mean the end to their bloodlines and their name.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.71,0:37:33.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我这辈子 都在潮头岛坚定捍卫哥哥的统治\N{\fs40}I have spent my entire life on Driftmark defending my brother's seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.54,0:37:37.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我是科利斯大人的至亲 我们血脉同源\N{\fs40}I am Lord Corlys's closest kin, his own blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.34,0:37:41.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我的血管里流淌着真正的 不容置疑的瓦列利安之血\N{\fs40}The true, unimpeachable blood of House Velaryon runs through my veins.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.55,0:37:45.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我的儿子们也是如此 他们是兰尼诺·瓦列利安的孩子\N{\fs40}As it does in my sons, the offspring of Laenor Velaryon.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.64,0:37:48.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果你真的在意家族血脉 魏蒙德爵士\N{\fs40}If you cared so much about your house's blood, Ser Vaemond,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.52,0:37:50.65,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你就不该如此大胆 妄图取代家族的合法继承人\N{\fs40}you would not be so bold as to supplant its rightful heir.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.73,0:37:54.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你的说辞不过是为了个人利益和野心\N{\fs40}No, you only speak for yourself and for your own ambition.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.19,0:37:56.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,稍候会有机会让你表达诉求 雷妮拉公主\N{\fs40}You will have chance to make your own petition, Princess Rhaenyra.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.77,0:37:59.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,请尊重魏蒙德爵士 听完他的发言\N{\fs40}Do Ser Vaemond the courtesy of allowing his to be heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.32,0:38:07.86,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,公主 你对瓦列利安的血脉了解多少?\N{\fs40}What do you know of Velaryon blood, Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.33,0:38:12.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就算我割开血管让你看看\N{\fs40}I could cut my veins and show it to you
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.42,0:38:15.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你也认不出来\N{\fs40}and you still wouldn't recognize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.71,0:38:19.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,此事关乎我们家族的未来和存亡 与你无关\N{\fs40}This is about the future and survival of my house, not yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.76,0:38:26.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,王后陛下 首相大人\N{\fs40}My Queen, my Lord Hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.22,0:38:31.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这是血脉传承的问题 无关野心\N{\fs40}This is a matter of blood, not ambition.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.48,0:38:37.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我把家族存亡和血脉延续置于一切之上\N{\fs40}I place the continuation of the survival of my house and my line above all.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.36,0:38:40.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我谦卑地向各位提名自己\N{\fs40}I humbly put myself before you as my brother's successor...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.69,0:38:45.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,作为我的兄长 潮头岛伯爵 潮汛之主的继承人\N{\fs40}the Lord of Driftmark and Lord of the Tides.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.32,0:38:47.86,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,感谢你的发言 魏蒙德爵士\N{\fs40}Thank you, Ser Vaemond.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.00,0:39:00.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮拉公主 现在可以为你的儿子路斯里斯·瓦列利安发言了\N{\fs40}Princess Rhaenyra, you may now speak for your son, Lucerys Velaryon.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.84,0:39:08.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果面对这场闹剧 我还非得说点什么\N{\fs40}If I am to grace this farce with some answer,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.60,0:39:12.15,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那我首先要提醒各位 大约二十年前 就在这个——\N{\fs40}I will start by reminding the court that nearly 20 years ago, in this very--
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.48,0:39:20.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,坦格利安家族的\N{\fs40}King Viserys of House Targaryen,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.52,0:39:22.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,韦赛里斯一世\N{\fs40}the First of His Name,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.61,0:39:25.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,安达尔人 洛伊拿人\N{\fs40}King of the Andals, and the Rhoynar,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.86,0:39:27.99,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,和先民的国王\N{\fs40}and the First Men,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.07,0:39:32.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,七国统治者暨全境守护者 驾到！\N{\fs40}Lord of the Seven Kingdoms, and Protector of the Realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.53,0:40:54.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,今天我来坐铁王座\N{\fs40}I will sit the throne today.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.33,0:40:57.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陛下\N{\fs40}Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.88,0:41:07.76,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我没事 我没事\N{\fs40}I will be fine. I will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.52,0:41:23.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我说了我没事\N{\fs40}I said I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.78,0:41:27.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 啊……   - 来吧\N{\fs40}-Ah... -Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.28,0:41:36.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,稳住\N{\fs40}Steady.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.08,0:42:23.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我必须……承认……我很疑惑\N{\fs40}I must... admit... my confusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.25,0:42:27.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我不理解\N{\fs40}I do not understand
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.59,0:42:31.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,继承人早已定下 还要陈什么情\N{\fs40}why petitions are being heard over a settled succession.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.01,0:42:33.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在场唯一……\N{\fs40}The only one present...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.39,0:42:38.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,真正了解科利斯大人意愿的人\N{\fs40}who might offer keener insight into Lord Corlys's wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.06,0:42:40.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是雷妮丝公主\N{\fs40}is the Princess Rhaenys.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.60,0:42:46.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,确实如此 陛下\N{\fs40}Indeed, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.08,0:43:03.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我丈夫一直都希望潮头岛\N{\fs40}It was ever my husband's will that Driftmark
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.29,0:43:05.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,由兰尼诺爵士的\N{\fs40}pass through Ser Laenor
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.04,0:43:07.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,亲生儿子继承……\N{\fs40}to his trueborn son...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.79,0:43:10.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,也就是路斯里斯·瓦列利安\N{\fs40}Lucerys Velaryon.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.96,0:43:12.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他的想法从未改变\N{\fs40}His mind never changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.72,0:43:15.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我对他的支持也从未改变\N{\fs40}Nor did my support of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.01,0:43:20.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,事实上 雷妮拉公主刚刚向我表达了她的意愿\N{\fs40}As a matter of fact, the Princess Rhaenyra has just informed me of her desire
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.26,0:43:22.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她希望她的儿子 小杰和小路\N{\fs40}to marry her sons Jace and Luke
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.47,0:43:25.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,与科利斯大人的外孙女 贝妮拉和雷妮亚订下婚约\N{\fs40}to Lord Corlys's granddaughters, Baela and Rhaena.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.27,0:43:30.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我真心实意赞同这门亲事\N{\fs40}A proposal to which I heartily agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.36,0:43:34.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那……就这么定了\N{\fs40}Well... the matter is settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.24,0:43:37.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我再重申一遍\N{\fs40}Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.74,0:43:44.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,确立瓦列利安家族的路斯里斯王子\N{\fs40}I hereby reaffirm Prince Lucerys of House Velaryon
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.12,0:43:46.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,为潮头岛和浮木王座的继承人\N{\fs40}as heir to Driftmark,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.37,0:43:51.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,暨下一任潮汛之主\N{\fs40}the Driftwood Throne, and the next Lord of the Tides.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.76,0:43:59.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你违反了法律……\N{\fs40}You break law...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.55,0:44:03.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,破坏了延续几个世纪的传统\N{\fs40}and centuries of tradition
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.27,0:44:05.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,让你的女儿做继承人\N{\fs40}to install your daughter as heir.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.60,0:44:08.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但你休想告诉我……\N{\fs40}Yet you dare tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.27,0:44:12.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,谁有资格做瓦列利安的继承人\N{\fs40}who deserves to inherit the name Velaryon.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.53,0:44:15.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不行\N{\fs40}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.95,0:44:19.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我决不允许\N{\fs40}I will not allow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.07,0:44:21.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,“允许”?\N{\fs40}"Allow it"?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.66,0:44:24.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,别忘了你的身份 魏蒙德\N{\fs40}Do not forget yourself, Vaemond.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.71,0:44:33.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他不是真正的瓦列利安族人\N{\fs40}That is no true Velaryon,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.46,0:44:36.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,也绝对不是我的侄孙\N{\fs40}and certainly no nephew of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.97,0:44:39.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,退下吧 你说得够多了\N{\fs40}Go to your chambers. You have said enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.26,0:44:43.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,路斯里斯是我的亲生外孙\N{\fs40}Lucerys is my true-born grandson.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.72,0:44:46.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而你……\N{\fs40}And you...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.39,0:44:49.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,只不过是潮头岛的次子而已\N{\fs40}are no more than the second son of Driftmark.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.90,0:44:55.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你……可以随意安排你的家族\N{\fs40}You... may run your house as you see fit...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.57,0:44:59.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但是你不能决定我家族的未来\N{\fs40}but you will not decide the future of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.57,0:45:03.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我的家族从末日浩劫中幸存\N{\fs40}My house survived the Doom
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.91,0:45:06.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,历经千百次磨难\N{\fs40}and a thousand tribulations besides.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.70,0:45:08.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,诸神见鬼去吧……\N{\fs40}And gods be damned...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.92,0:45:15.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我绝不会看着我的家族灭亡于这个——\N{\fs40}I will not see it ended on the account of this--
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.17,0:45:18.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,说出来\N{\fs40}Say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.31,0:45:30.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她的孩子……\N{\fs40}Her children...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.56,0:45:33.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是野种!\N{\fs40}are bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.07,0:45:38.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她……\N{\fs40}And she...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.36,0:45:40.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是个……\N{\fs40}is...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.20,0:45:42.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,婊子\N{\fs40}a whore.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.16,0:45:50.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我要……\N{\fs40}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.87,0:45:53.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,割了你的舌头\N{\fs40}will have your tongue for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.05,0:46:03.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,还是留着他的舌头吧\N{\fs40}He can keep his tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.39,0:46:05.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 拿下他的武器！- 不必了\N{\fs40}-Disarm him! -No need.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.56,0:46:15.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 叫学士来！- 父亲？\N{\fs40}-Call the maesters! -Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.81,0:46:18.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,求你了亲爱的 你得喝点什么来止痛\N{\fs40}Please, my love. You must take something for the pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.61,0:46:22.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我现在不能神智不清\N{\fs40}I will not cloud my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.28,0:46:24.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我得让事情回到正轨\N{\fs40}I must put things right.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.87,0:47:14.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,遗体明日即可启程送回潮头岛了 夫人\N{\fs40}The body will be ready for its return to Driftmark on the morrow, my lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.17,0:47:21.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您可以让静默姐妹自己完成工作\N{\fs40}You may wish to leave the Silent Sisters to their work.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.26,0:47:23.80,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,直面死亡不大吉利\N{\fs40}It is ill luck to look upon the face of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.14,0:47:32.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我已经数不清见过陌客多少次了 大学士\N{\fs40}The Stranger has visited me more times than I can count, Grand Maester.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.98,0:47:38.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我敢说\N{\fs40}I assure you...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.65,0:47:43.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他其实根本不在乎我是睁眼还是闭眼\N{\fs40}he cares little whether my eyes are open or closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.95,0:49:12.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,今晚见到你们……齐聚一堂……\N{\fs40}How good it is... to see you all tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.49,0:49:14.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我真高兴\N{\fs40}together.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.75,0:49:23.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 要餐前祈祷吗？ - 好\N{\fs40}-Prayer before we begin? -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.71,0:49:27.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,愿圣母慈爱的目光 欢笑着注视我们齐聚一堂\N{\fs40}May the Mother smile down on this gathering with love.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.09,0:49:31.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,愿铁匠修补我们断裂已久的纽带\N{\fs40}May the Smith mend the bonds that have been broken for far too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.80,0:49:35.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,至于魏蒙德·瓦列利安 愿诸神赐予他安息\N{\fs40}And to Vaemond Velaryon, may the gods give him rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.15,0:49:46.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,今天也是个值得庆祝的时刻\N{\fs40}This is an occasion for celebration, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.03,0:49:49.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我的外孙们 小杰和小路\N{\fs40}My grandsons, Jace and Luke,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.53,0:49:52.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,会迎娶他们的表亲 贝妮拉与雷妮亚\N{\fs40}will marry their cousins, Baela and Rhaena,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.86,0:49:56.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这使我们的家族血脉更加紧密相连\N{\fs40}further strengthening the bond between our houses.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.24,0:49:59.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,敬年轻的王子们……\N{\fs40}A toast to the young Princes...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.79,0:50:02.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 与他们的未婚妻 - 干杯 干杯！\N{\fs40}-and their betrothed. -Hear, hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.29,0:50:05.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不错啊小杰 你终于能睡女人了\N{\fs40}Well done, Jace. You'll finally get to lie with a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.92,0:50:10.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,让我们敬路斯里斯王子……\N{\fs40}Let us toast as well Prince Lucerys...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.30,0:50:14.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,未来的高潮城伯爵\N{\fs40}the future Lord of the Tides.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.18,0:50:15.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,干杯 干杯\N{\fs40}Hear, hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.55,0:50:17.09,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你会成为大人物\N{\fs40}You'll be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.68,0:50:25.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我猜 你知道那事儿该怎么干 对吧？\N{\fs40}You do know how the act is done, I assume?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.15,0:50:26.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,至少懂点儿理论吧？\N{\fs40}At least in principle?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.40,0:50:27.86,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,该把鸡巴放哪儿啊啥的\N{\fs40}Where to put your cock and all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.94,0:50:29.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,别理他 表哥\N{\fs40}Let it be, cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.36,0:50:33.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你要想扮演弄臣 那随意 但在我未婚妻面前最好管住你的嘴\N{\fs40}You can play the jester if you wish, but hold your tongue before my betrothed.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.72,0:50:59.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我既是满心欢喜\N{\fs40}It both gladdens my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.22,0:51:03.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,又充满悲伤\N{\fs40}and fills me with sorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.48,0:51:06.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,只因见到你们齐聚于此\N{\fs40}to see these faces around the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.02,0:51:11.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你们都是我在这个世界上最亲近的人……\N{\fs40}The faces most dear to me in all the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.15,0:51:15.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但在过去的多年中 你们彼此却……\N{\fs40}yet grown so distant from each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.49,0:51:18.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,渐行渐远 充满隔阂\N{\fs40}in the years past.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.35,0:51:44.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我这张脸……\N{\fs40}My own face...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.98,0:51:47.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,早已不复往昔的英俊……\N{\fs40}is no longer a handsome one...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.98,0:51:51.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果以前还算英俊的话\N{\fs40}if indeed it ever was.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.11,0:51:56.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但是今晚……\N{\fs40}But tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.28,0:52:00.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我希望你们看到的是我……我本人\N{\fs40}I wish you to see me... as I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.08,0:52:03.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不仅仅是君主……\N{\fs40}Not just a king...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.33,0:52:06.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而是你们的父亲\N{\fs40}but your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.25,0:52:09.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,兄弟\N{\fs40}Your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.21,0:52:11.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,丈夫……\N{\fs40}Your husband...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.17,0:52:15.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,和外公\N{\fs40}and your grandsire.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.88,0:52:19.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一个 似乎……\N{\fs40}Who may not, it seems...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.05,0:52:21.97,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,已经行将就木的老人\N{\fs40}walk for much longer among you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.69,0:52:32.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,让我们心中不要再充满恶意\N{\fs40}Let us no longer hold ill feelings in our hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.48,0:52:35.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,若龙王家族内部分崩离析\N{\fs40}The crown cannot stand strong
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.28,0:52:37.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,王权则难以稳固\N{\fs40}if the House of the Dragon remains divided.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.86,0:52:41.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,放下心中的不满吧\N{\fs40}But set aside your grievances.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.12,0:52:47.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,哪怕不是为了王权……\N{\fs40}if not for the sake of the crown...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.33,0:52:50.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而是为了我这个\N{\fs40}then for the sake of this old man
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.46,0:52:53.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,爱你们至深的\N{\fs40}who loves you all
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.05,0:52:55.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,老人\N{\fs40}so dearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.57,0:53:25.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我想举杯敬王后陛下\N{\fs40}I wish to raise my cup to Her Grace, the Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.75,0:53:31.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我爱我的父亲\N{\fs40}I love my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.21,0:53:34.76,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但我得承认 没人能像……\N{\fs40}But I must admit that no one has stood...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.67,0:53:38.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他身旁的妻子那样对他忠诚\N{\fs40}more loyally by his side than his good wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.43,0:53:43.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,多年来她辛苦照料……\N{\fs40}She has tended to him with...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.43,0:53:46.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,用始终如一的奉献精神\N{\fs40}unfailing devotion,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.68,0:53:49.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,爱 与尊敬\N{\fs40}love, and honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.60,0:53:53.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,为此 我对她心怀感激……\N{\fs40}And for that, she has my gratitude...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.02,0:53:56.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,和歉意\N{\fs40}and my apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.87,0:54:08.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你的宽厚让我动容 公主\N{\fs40}Your graciousness moves me deeply, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.12,0:54:13.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们都是母亲……\N{\fs40}We are both mothers...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.38,0:54:18.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,都深爱着自己的孩子\N{\fs40}and we love our children.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.68,0:54:24.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,即使有时不愿承认 但我们其实有很多共同点\N{\fs40}We have more in common than we sometimes allow.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.81,0:54:31.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我敬你和你的家族\N{\fs40}I raise my cup to you and to your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.40,0:54:38.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你会是个好女王\N{\fs40}You will make a fine queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.35,0:55:15.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我……\N{\fs40}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.56,0:55:19.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我为你即将忍受的失望而感到遗憾\N{\fs40}I regret the disappointment you are soon to suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.03,0:55:23.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但如果你想感受一下真正的满足\N{\fs40}But if you ever wish to know what it is to be well satisfied,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.53,0:55:25.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我乐意随时效劳\N{\fs40}all you have to do is ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.28,0:55:27.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,小杰\N{\fs40}Jace.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.02,0:56:00.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,敬伊耿和伊蒙德王子\N{\fs40}To Prince Aegon and Prince Aemond.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.27,0:56:03.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,虽然我们多年未见\N{\fs40}We have not seen each other in years,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.65,0:56:06.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但年少时一起成长的时光我记忆犹新\N{\fs40}but I have fond memories of our shared youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.82,0:56:12.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,作为男人 希望我们可以既是朋友 又是同盟\N{\fs40}And as men, I hope we may yet be friends and allies.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.87,0:56:16.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,愿你和你的家庭健康常在 亲爱的舅舅们\N{\fs40}To you and your family's good health, dear uncles.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.34,0:56:25.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,也敬你\N{\fs40}To you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.31,0:56:35.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,且牢记 木板底 凶兽起\N{\fs40}Beware the beast beneath the boards.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.81,0:56:37.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,干得好 孩子\N{\fs40}Well done, my boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.31,0:56:40.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我想敬贝妮拉和雷妮亚\N{\fs40}I would like to toast to Baela and Rhaena.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.69,0:56:42.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她们即将走入婚姻\N{\fs40}They'll be married soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.78,0:56:46.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,其实没那么糟 大多数时间他只是无视你而已……\N{\fs40}It isn't so bad. Mostly he just ignores you...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.15,0:56:50.03,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,喝醉的时候例外\N{\fs40}except sometimes when he's drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.58,0:57:01.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 挺好 - 来点音乐吧\N{\fs40}-Good. -Let us have some music.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.22,0:57:08.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不好意思\N{\fs40}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.23,0:58:42.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,护卫\N{\fs40}Guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.03,0:58:51.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,请坐\N{\fs40}Please, sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.90,0:59:32.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,最后的致敬\N{\fs40}Final tribute.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.32,0:59:37.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,愿我的外甥们身体健康\N{\fs40}To the health of my nephews:
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.20,0:59:39.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,小杰\N{\fs40}Jace...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.83,0:59:42.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,小路\N{\fs40}Luke...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.08,0:59:44.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,和乔佛里\N{\fs40}and Joffrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.71,0:59:49.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,愿他们每一位都英俊 智慧……\N{\fs40}Each of them handsome, wise...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.30,0:59:57.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 如斯强壮 - 伊蒙德\N{\fs40}-strong. -Aemond.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.80,0:59:58.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,来……\N{\fs40}Come...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.68,1:00:04.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,让我们干杯 为三个……\N{\fs40}let us drain our cups to these three...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.98,1:00:07.15,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 如斯强壮的男孩们 - 你敢再说一次\N{\fs40}-Strong boys. -I dare you to say that again.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.23,1:00:10.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,怎么了？不过是一句恭维罢了\N{\fs40}Why? 'Twas only a compliment.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.40,1:00:11.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你觉得自己不够壮吗？\N{\fs40}Do you not think yourself Strong?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.65,1:00:14.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 小杰！- 够了！\N{\fs40}-Jace! -That is enough!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.62,1:00:23.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你干嘛当着这么多人的面说这些？\N{\fs40}Why would you say such a thing before these people?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.70,1:00:26.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我只是表达一下对家族的自豪罢了 母亲\N{\fs40}I was merely expressing how proud I am of my family, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.96,1:00:30.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但好像我的外甥们对自己的家族没有那么多自豪感啊\N{\fs40}Mm, though it seems my nephews aren't quite as proud of theirs.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.79,1:00:32.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,等等 站住\N{\fs40}Wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.30,1:00:39.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,回你们房间去 所有人 立刻\N{\fs40}Go to your quarters. All of you go, now.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.24,1:00:59.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮拉\N{\fs40}Rhaenyra.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.83,1:01:06.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我觉得 我们最好还是先回龙石岛吧\N{\fs40}It's best, I think, if we go back to Dragonstone.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.54,1:01:08.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你才刚来不久\N{\fs40}You've only just arrived.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.55,1:01:16.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,让我送孩子们回去\N{\fs40}Let me see the children home.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.34,1:01:18.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我会……\N{\fs40}I'll...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.09,1:01:21.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,骑着龙再回来\N{\fs40}return on dragonback.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.22,1:01:28.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陛下和我都希望如此\N{\fs40}The King and I would both like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.98,1:02:13.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,看样子今天的城堡之夜挺难熬啊\N{\fs40}It's been quite a night at the castle, it seems
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.48,1:02:15.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是的 夫人\N{\fs40}Yes, my lady.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.81,1:02:52.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,来 来\N{\fs40}Come on, come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.27,1:02:58.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,够了\N{\fs40}That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.83,1:03:08.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,噢...\N{\fs40}Oh...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.33,1:03:11.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fs40}Well done.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.46,1:03:20.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 抱歉 - 嘘\N{\fs40}-I'm sorry. -Shh.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.71,1:03:23.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 抱歉 - 嘘 嘘\N{\fs40}-I'm sorry. -Shh, shh, shh.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.22,1:03:27.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你想知道……\N{\fs40}But you wanted to know...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.14,1:03:30.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我是否相信\N{\fs40}if I believe it to be true.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.18,1:03:34.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,相信什么 陛下？\N{\fs40}Believe what to be true, my King?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.02,1:03:36.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你不记得了吗？\N{\fs40}Don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.48,1:03:39.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,伊耿……\N{\fs40}Aegon...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.32,1:03:43.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们的儿子？\N{\fs40}Our son?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.74,1:03:47.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他的梦\N{\fs40}His Dream.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.87,1:03:51.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,冰与火……之歌——\N{\fs40}The Song of Ice... and Fi--
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.50,1:03:54.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是真的\N{\fs40}It is true.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.08,1:03:57.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他于北方所见\N{\fs40}What he saw in the North.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.50,1:04:01.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,预言中的王子\N{\fs40}The Prince That Was Promised.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.71,1:04:03.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我听不懂 韦赛里斯\N{\fs40}I don't understand, Viserys.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.47,1:04:07.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那个王子\N{\fs40}The Prince.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.13,1:04:08.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,伊耿王子？\N{\fs40}Prince Aegon?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.97,1:04:11.76,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,将联合王国上下\N{\fs40}To unite the realm
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.85,1:04:14.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,抵御寒冷……与长夜\N{\fs40}against the cold... and the dark.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.73,1:04:20.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是你啊\N{\fs40}It is you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.03,1:04:24.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你就是那个人\N{\fs40}You are the one.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.70,1:04:28.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你一定要做到\N{\fs40}You must do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.37,1:04:32.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你一定要做到\N{\fs40}You must do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.95,1:05:18.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我明白了 陛下\N{\fs40}I understand, my King.
